query:
SELECT u.id as user_id, u.name, u.email, c.id as company_id, c.name as company_name, r.id as romaneio_id, r.title as romaneio_title, i.id as inspection_id, i.title as inspection_title, dt.id as term_id, dt.protocolNumber
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN companies c ON c.ownerId = u.id
LEFT JOIN romaneios r ON r.userId = u.id
LEFT JOIN inspections i ON i.userId = u.id
LEFT JOIN deliveryTerms dt ON dt.userId = u.id
WHERE u.openId = 'test-user-001'
LIMIT 1;
